<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.6">
<l>kaḷḷār tuḻāyuṅ kaṇavalaruṅ kūviḷaiyum</l>
<l>muḷḷār muḷariyu māmpalumuṉ kaṇṭakkāl</l>
<l>puḷḷāyō rēṉamāyp pukkiṭantāṉ poṉṉaṭikkeṉ</l>
<l>ṟuḷḷātā ruḷḷattai yuḷḷamāk koḷḷōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The minds of those who do not consider,</l>
<l rend="indent">[even] when they see before [them] nectar-filled tulasī,</l>
<l>Oleander, bilva [leaves], lotuses [with their leaves] covered with thorns,</l>
<l rend="indent">and water lilies,</l>
<l>That these are for the golden feet of him who rooted into [the earth]</l>
<l rend="indent">as a boar,</l>
<l>Having become a bird, we do not take as minds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
